      <item>
        <title>Editando o GRUB</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cuidado:&lt;/strong&gt; Não é muito bom editar o GRUB, mas de vez em quando a gente precisa.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Neste exemplo vou editar somente o &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;timeout&lt;/code&gt; para 5 seg.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Faça um &lt;strong&gt;backup&lt;/strong&gt; do grub. Senão já era.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;cp /etc/default/grub /etc/default/grub_ori
sudo gedit /etc/default/grub&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot; data-lang=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;GRUB_TIMEOUT&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Depois&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-vim&quot; data-lang=&quot;vim&quot;&gt;GRUB_TIMEOUT&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Salva e fecha. E no terminal digite&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;sudo update-grub&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pronto!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/img/posts/grub-update.png&quot; alt=&quot;grub-update.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fonte:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.howtogeek.com/196655/how-to-configure-the-grub2-boot-loaders-settings/&quot;&gt;how-to-configure-the-grub2-boot-loaders-settings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
